      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.6333334923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "りょ、旅行って……\nそんな、いきなり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.5333334923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.4333334923
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01-lim001.m4a",
      "text": "安心しろ、もう新幹線と宿は押さえてる\n芸能人御用達、口が堅いお忍び向きの老舗旅館――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.4333334923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "そういう問題じゃなくて！\nなんで旅行なんですか。それも、朝倉社長と……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.2333334923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私としても、説明を願いたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.2333334923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どういうことだ、これは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.500000159
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01-lmn002.m4a",
      "text": "順番にご説明します\nいったん朝倉さんは、そちらでお待ち下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.5666642825
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "……これが、荒療治ってことですか？\nブレイクスルーのための……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.1666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.4333306949
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01-lim002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、そうだ。けどな……\nただ旅行すりゃいいって訳じゃねぇぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.3333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.5999955814
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01-lmn003.m4a",
      "text": "三人にはそれぞれ、達成すべき課題を出すわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.5999955814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.8999935469
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "課題……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.8999935469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.6666602136
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 62.5666641235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01-lmn004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。まずはすみれ。あなたは朝倉さんに……\n全力でおねだりして、お土産を買ってもらいなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0333287557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.0333287557
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.1333268803
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "……はい？\nお、おねだり……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.9666620891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.0333268803
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01-lim003.m4a",
      "text": "次は優だ。お前は一回でいいから\n全力で朝倉さんを大爆笑させろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.9333287557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.3666576704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "……大……爆笑……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.3666576704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.2666576704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01-lim004.m4a",
      "text": "んで、瑠依は朝倉さんに向けて\n真正面から「パパ」って呼んでやれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4666595459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.4666595459
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.3333243371
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "パ……えぇっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.3333243371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.5999910038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょ、ちょ～っと待ってもらっていいです？\n念のため……ふざけては……いませんよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.7666595459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.7666595459
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.8333243371
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01-lmn005.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前よ。納得のいく理由を話しておく？\n順番に、すみれから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.6999928792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.1499910038
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 108.3999910038
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.4333243389
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01-lmn006.m4a",
      "text": "あなたは普段から、周りに合わせようと背伸びをし過ぎ\n年齢の割に大人ぶり過ぎなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.8999949137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.8999949137
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.1833243371
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.1833243371
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01-lmn007.m4a",
      "text": "悪いことじゃないわ。けど精神的な殻を破るには\nありのままの飾らない自分を受け入れることが必要よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.633328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.2999910038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "ありのままの、飾らない自分……\n確かに、抑え込みがちだった……かも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.933328247,
      "sfxList": []
